title: For Sale/Trade:  Mosin Nagant M91 (3)
postcontent:
Up for sale or trade are three Mosin Nagant M91's. These are not the Mosin Nagant 91/30 which was the re-design in 1930. This is the orginal model rifle. 
All three are complete, including upper handguard and cleaning rods. 

The first is a 1915 Russian Peter the Great. This rifle is SA marked, meaning that Finland captured the rifle from the Russians, and the rifle passed Finn inspection, and was placed into service. This rifle was built at the Tula factory as well. Not a numbers matching, but I am firm on 325 for this rifle.  THIS IS SOLD - thanks Ken !

The second rifle is a 1942 Tikka. This is the original Russian model, put together by the Finns during the WWII effort. The bolt and barrel serial numbers match. This is a great shooter, and I am firm on 350 for this rifle.

The third rifle is the gem I have in regard to Mosin Nagants - this is a US built Westinghouse. The barrel is dated 1915, however my understanding is that all Westinghouse rifles built between 1915-1917 were dated 1915. The barrel and buttplate are numbers matching, but this is a great American built 7.62x54R rifle with a lineage to Pittsburgh... I am asking 375 for the rifle.    SOLD

I would be glad to meet you in Cranberry, or somewhere near PIT airport, Moon Township, or near Beaver Valley Mall / Monaca / Rochester. I also am in Squirrel Hill on Tuesday and Thursday nights, and Sundays. I also am in Harmarville on Sundays.

Baikal is a brand developed by IGP around which a series of shotgun products were developed from 1962. After the collapse of the USSR, commercial gun manufacture was greatly expanded under the Baikal brand.

I put Truglo Tritium/Fiber Optic (TFO) sights with front sight green and rear sight yellow, a magwell and the internals are polished for a smother trigger pull. I have put 250 rounds of white box Winchester through it and had no problems. I will require a bill of sell for my personal records since I bought the gun when I was living in California and it is registered to me. The gun is in excellent condition.
